♪Thinking of you,
the sky turns light blue♪

2
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:24,620
♪Thinking of you,
the sunlight feels gentle♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,820
♪Thinking of you, the clouds look pink♪

4
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:33,140
♪One bite, so sweet♪

5
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:40,660
♪Loving you
is like honey melting in the sun♪

6
00:00:40,900 --> 00:00:44,900
♪Even the coldest winter feels warm♪

7
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:50,780
♪Since falling for you,
I only want your company♪

8
00:00:51,060 --> 00:00:54,940
♪You see through
all my sweet little schemes♪

9
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:57,340
♪What should I do?♪

10
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:06,100
[My Sassy Girl]

11
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,100
[Episode 13]

12
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,520
Hope to see you again.

13
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,360
Do you have paintings to sell?

14
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:22,000
We have a favor to ask.

15
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,760
Please check this painting.

16
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:30,520
Where did you get it?

17
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:31,920
Listen carefully.

18
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,240
You'd better get rid of it soon.

19
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,480
Do you know it?

20
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,880
It's the burial object accompanying
the daughter of the Grand Tutor.

21
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,360
After the daughter died,

22
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,200
her soul entered into the painting.

23
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,440
Later on,

24
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,040
her tomb was robbed,

25
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,480
which liberated this eerie painting.

26
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,360
It has caused many mishaps

27
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,440
over a decade.

28
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,680
Whoever has it

29
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,520
will burn himself to death.

30
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:01,640
A malicious object it is indeed.

31
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,440
It's as ominous as the devil.

32
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,480
It was his daughter again.

33
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,440
Do you have any idea

34
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,360
who the painter was?

35
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,320
Well.

36
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,400
It was the prominent Paint Saint,

37
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,880
Ye Qingshan's work.

38
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,680
But,

39
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,920
he has been silenced for a long time.

40
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,880
Does he have anyone close to him?

41
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,480
You see.

42
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,320
I'm only a merchant.

43
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:30,880
The source is not my merchandise.

44
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:35,800
But you can make it one,

45
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,360
can't you?

46
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:42,000
Ye Qingshan does have an apprentice.

47
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:42,880
But half a year ago,

48
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:45,440
he moved to the suburbs of the capital.

49
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,480
Who is it?

50
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,320
Luo Hanshui

51
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,320
of the Yunshan Painting Gallery.

52
00:02:55,940 --> 00:03:00,700
[Yunshan Painting Gallery]

53
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,440
Excuse me.

54
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,240
This way, please.

55
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,480
It's your first time here.

56
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,940
Do you know our rules?

57
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,720
I'm all ears.

58
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,460
Mr. Luo is good at drawing beauties.

59
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,980
But he has two rules.

60
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,120
One, it's free to draw

61
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,060
for a beauty.

62
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,560
Two, he won't do business with merchants

63
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,320
no matter how much they offer.

64
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,480
The first one

65
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,520
is reasonable.

66
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,360
But the second one...

67
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,640
Doesn't he want to make money?

68
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,320
Mr. Luo is not trying to sell them.

69
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,700
Besides,

70
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,840
he hates those rich men the most.

71
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,360
Even if they are fabulously wealthy,

72
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,760
they still have a lowbrow taste.

73
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,440
And they are in no place

74
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,160
to judge his works.

75
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,120
Good.

76
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,840
A man of integrity.

77
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,280
Master Luo

78
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,060
really deserves his fame.

79
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,600
He is just flattering.

80
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,040
Don't take it for real.

81
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,000
A word of compliment won't kill you.

82
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,560
Guys.

83
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,440
Please.

84
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,120
This way.

85
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,520
Mr. Luo is out
looking for painting sceneries.

86
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,760
He should be back

87
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:21,680
in no time.

88
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,400
Have some rest.

89
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,680
I won't be bothering.

90
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,040
Right.

91
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:45,060
[The summer of the Year of Guisi,
Yunshan Painting Gallery by Luo Hanshui]

92
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:46,480
Alas.

93
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,560
I'm getting hungry.

94
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,040
When will he be back?

95
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,360
We've been waiting for so long.

96
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,440
Sorry to keep you waiting.

97
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,400
I'm sorry.

98
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,600
Please.

99
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:15,040
[Luo Hanshui, Painter]

100
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,280
My servant told me

101
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,840
the lady here wants me

102
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,360
to draw her a painting.

103
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,560
I guess you two

104
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,000
have already known about my rules.

105
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,000
To be honest,

106
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,720
besides painting,

107
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,720
there's one more thing

108
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,840
I'd like to ask you for.

109
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:32,840
Oh?

110
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,000
I recently acquired a famous painting.

111
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,560
And I deeply cherish it.

112
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,200
I've heard

113
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,400
that it was from your school.

114
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,960
I wonder if you recognize it.

115
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,400
Please put it back, Sir.

116
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,760
No.

117
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:52,800
You'd better burn it.

118
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,960
Was the painting

119
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,440
your master

120
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,280
Ye Qingshan's work?

121
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,560
To tell you the truth,

122
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,800
it was indeed my master's work.

123
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,640
But he devoted all his life to skills.

124
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:11,520
All the aristocrats begged for his work.

125
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,520
And this Snow Spirit Painting

126
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,160
was eventually given to Grand Tutor Ji.

127
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,160
And his daughter was deeply fond of it.

128
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,440
Folks' rumor had it

129
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,640
that after she died,

130
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,040
her soul entered into the painting.

131
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,760
So,

132
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,800
it's better to burn it.

133
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,520
It's merely a painting.

134
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,480
How could it do the harm?

135
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,000
I don't know about that.

136
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,200
But,

137
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,880
the painting

138
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:43,200
is truly different from the normal ones.

139
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,760
The pigments were thickly applied.

140
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,160
It's so vivid.

141
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,760
Master Luo,

142
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:49,960
what was that painting skill?

143
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,120
Can you do it?

144
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,480
It was a unique skill of my master.

145
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,320
I'm not smart enough

146
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,480
to master it.

147
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,120
Guys.

148
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,200
Do you want me to paint or not?

149
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,120
Sure.

150
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,280
Master Luo.

151
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,160
Please draw a painting for my wife.

152
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,440
Five thousand taels of silver.

153
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,680
What?

154
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,400
Five thousand taels?

155
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,520
Where is that coming from?

156
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,320
Um...

157
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,880
What Master Luo means

158
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,720
is that the drawing paper

159
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:52,840
is worth the price.

160
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:54,880
What I mean is...

161
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,040
You mean

162
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,080
the pigments are five thousand taels.

163
00:07:59,160 --> 00:07:59,680
Right.

164
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,440
The pigments.

165
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,600
Am I right?

166
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,560
Master Luo.

167
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,040
With all due respect,

168
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,720
what kind of women

169
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,840
will be free of charge?

170
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,080
This is Wen Ruoxi,
the daughter of Mr. Wen.

171
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,120
[Springtime of the Year of Ji Hai,
Yunshan Painting Gallery by Luo Hanshui]

172
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,800
She's graceful as a startled swan,

173
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,920
and agile as a flying dragon.

174
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,600
Such a stunning beauty.

175
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,560
I'd paint her for the rest of my life

176
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,560
without asking for a dime.

177
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,760
What a beauty she is.

178
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,040
What do you think?

179
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,000
She's just average.

180
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,560
Not impressive.

181
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,720
Are you questioning my skill?

182
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,760
Never mind.

183
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,960
Only Miss Wen,

184
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,200
with such unparalleled beauty,

185
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,920
is worth the exquisite brushwork

186
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,480
of Master Luo.

187
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,880
I won't be bothering.

188
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:17,720
Farewell.

189
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,480
Goodbye.

190
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,440
Two ridiculous rules.

191
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,320
It's just a means to fame and fortune.

192
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,440
Don't take it seriously.

193
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,600
There is nothing to be upset about.

194
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,680
Me and Miss Wen

195
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,240
are just like mud and clouds.

196
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,880
Beauty is in the eye of the beholder.

197
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,000
You don't have to compete with her.

198
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,160
You sure have a way with words.

199
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,640
Let's get back to the case.

200
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,200
Any progress?

201
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,880
It is almost certain

202
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,920
that Luo Hanshui bears prejudice
against merchants.

203
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,920
There must be something behind it.

204
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,280
Anything else?

205
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:08,880
And

206
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,800
his arms won't be this strong

207
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,880
just by painting.

208
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,640
He must be a man of martial arts.

209
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,600
I agree.

210
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:24,760
Luo Hanshui seems strange to me as well.

211
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,200
Let's take roles from storybooks
for example.

212
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,240
As a painter,

213
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,320
Luo Hanshui never draws animals.

214
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:35,920
His works are all about beauty.

215
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,320
He definitely is a pervert.

216
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,000
Maybe

217
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,720
he is the killer.

218
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,800
And it was for love.

219
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,400
What a typical deduction

220
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,560
by Lu Nanyi.

221
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:53,760
Anyway,

222
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,640
we won't figure it out now.

223
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,320
How about we get back to it tomorrow?

224
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:58,640
Okay.

225
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:01,500
[Little Wonton for Marriage]

226
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,800
Nanyi.

227
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,720
There.

228
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:06,640
After all these years,

229
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,440
this restaurant is still open.

230
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:11,000
I've been craving
for their fried wontons for so long.

231
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:15,920
Come on!

232
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:16,640
Qingqiu.

233
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,720
Sir.

234
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,040
Yes.

235
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:24,720
Two bowls of wontons.

236
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,280
OK!

237
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,880
Everything here is the same as before.

238
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,960
I remember

239
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,320
that back in the day,

240
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,320
you always took me here for wontons

241
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:36,400
whenever your parents scolded you.

242
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,400
People drink their sorrows away
with spirit.

243
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:39,400
But you

244
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,400
drank my wonton soup.

245
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,160
How could you say that?

246
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,200
You know that I don't like vinegar,

247
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:46,800
and you always added it on purpose.

248
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,200
Here you go.

249
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,880
Guys.

250
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,660
Wontons for marriage.

251
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,200
Enjoy.

252
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,760
Mr. Wu.

253
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:57,640
Miss Lu.

254
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,480
Mr. Lin.

255
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,320
I haven't seen you for so many years.

256
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,400
Mr. Wu,

257
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,320
your wonton is as popular as before.

258
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:04,880
Well.

259
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,560
Not bad.

260
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,920
Since we haven't met in many years,

261
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:09,360
these wontons are on the house.

262
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,760
No way.

263
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,920
Please take it.

264
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:13,920
It's on me.

265
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,160
Please don't, Mr. Wu.

266
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:15,800
Come on.

267
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,360
Take it.

268
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,160
I can't.

269
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,680
Mr. Wu.

270
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,840
Just take it.

271
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,160
Well,

272
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,160
I hope you two

273
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,400
have a lovely baby soon.

274
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,280
Just tell me if you want more.

275
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,160
Here.

276
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,000
Sir.

277
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,760
Something comes up.

278
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,280
Nanyi.

279
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,240
We should move.

280
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,120
Yes.

281
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,280
The Miracle Physician Huaigu
who can bring the dead back to life.

282
00:12:57,280 --> 00:13:00,280
The Miracle Physician Huaigu
who can bring the dead back to life.

283
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,680
The Miracle Physician Yu is here.

284
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,720
I wonder which dignitary is indisposed.

285
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,920
Ms. Zhu from the Qian Residence
has recently been poisoned.

286
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,560
The physicians in the capital
can't do anything about it.

287
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,800
The Lord Mayor is kind-hearted,

288
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,160
inviting a famous physician
to diagnose her.

289
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:14,880
Well,

290
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,040
it is the Miracle Physician Yu.

291
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:17,920
I don't know if he can cure her.

292
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,080
Absolutely he can.

293
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:24,800
Miss Lu.

294
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,440
I've been practicing for years.

295
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:29,200
And I've always kept a low profile.

296
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,520
Such flamboyant display

297
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:34,100
might attract criticism.

298
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,160
Mr. Yu.

299
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,560
It's the order of Mr. Lin.

300
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,440
I hope you can understand it.

301
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:50,460
[The Miracle Physician Huaigu
who can Bring the Dead Back to Life.]

302
00:13:51,140 --> 00:13:55,860
[Qian Residence]

303
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:13,480
Lin Qingqiu,

304
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:15,040
you are still in the mood for tea now?

305
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:21,480
So what else should I do?

306
00:14:22,640 --> 00:14:23,560
Wandering around like you?

307
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,440
You...!

308
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,680
Sir,

309
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:29,980
