310
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:30,680
I'm well.

311
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,880
Mr. Yu is truly

312
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,320
the Miracle Physician.

313
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,760
I can't believe you're cured in no time.

314
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,080
You're the one who tried out the poison.

315
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,000
You're the one looking for the killer.

316
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:43,880
And you drew everyone's attention
by getting Ms. Zhu a physician.

317
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:46,020
What's on your mind honestly?

318
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,080
Mr. Lei,

319
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,600
you're making better tea now.

320
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,200
Thank you, Sir.

321
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,000
