322
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,280
Don't be so hasty.

323
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,320
I arranged a big palanquin

324
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,760
for Mr. Yu

325
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,400
and had you spread the word.

326
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,880
For what?

327
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,840
To tempt the killer.

328
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,600
Lure him out?

329
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,440
Correct.

330
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,280
Mr. Yu.

331
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:21,440
How is it?

332
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:25,240
Alas.

333
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:28,160
The poison Mr. Lin took

334
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,120
is called Snow Cold Spider.

335
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:32,340
You'll be poisoned when touching it.

336
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:35,320
Mild symptom shows slight coldness

337
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,600
and illusion.

338
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:40,120
Occasionally touching it is fine.

339
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,840
But there will be toxic sediment

340
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,560
when touching it frequently.

341
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,840
Even if the Great Physician Hua Tuo

342
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,720
can't help him much.

343
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,000
But luckily,

344
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:57,000
he is a mild case.

345
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,040
And he's young and strong.

346
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:01,960
He'll be fine.

347
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:05,600
Mr. Yu,

348
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:08,080
the illusions they have,

349
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,040
are they different?

350
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,920
I've been infected once

351
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,680
and what I saw was different

352
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:16,240
from what Mr. Qian and Jiu did.

353
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,320
Well...

354
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,120
I don't know for sure.

355
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,400
The Grand Tutor Ji

356
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,480
was also poisoned once.

357
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,600
And I cured him.

358
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,200
I heard

359
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:32,680
that only the Paint Saint
and his apprentice have the antidote.

360
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,080
Then why did the rumors say

361
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,800
that it was his daughter
hiding inside the painting?

362
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,560
They are all fallacies.

363
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,400
His daughter

364
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:43,640
was born weak and vulnerable.

365
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,520
Her death
had nothing to do with the painting.

366
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,240
Her soul would not hide in the painting.

367
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,000
Alas.

368
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,600
May the dead rest in peace.

369
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:55,840
Mr. Yu,

370
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:57,200
