371
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:58,800
Sure.

372
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,680
So when you were poisoned,

373
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,240
did you see the ghost in the painting?

374
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,680
Are you all right?

375
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:20,760
Mr. Lin,

376
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,560
