377
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:24,240
Is it mildly cold

378
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,880
or freezing cold?

379
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,960
When you're poisoned,

380
00:18:29,120 --> 00:18:32,120
if you show slight coldness,
you'll be fear of cold.

381
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:35,080
If you feel freezing cold,
your body will shiver

382
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,200
and find it difficult to breathe.

383
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:37,880
If it's the former,

384
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,160
drink half of the medicine.

385
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,360
If it's the latter,

386
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,440
you have to drink it up.

387
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,960
If it's neither the former

388
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:44,880
nor the latter,

389
00:18:45,220 --> 00:18:46,360
