392
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:52,000
Mr. Lin?

393
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:53,680
Are you cold?

394
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:55,220
Mr. Lin?

395
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:58,000
Mr. Lin!

396
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,240
