397
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:02,120
Here.

398
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:04,200
You should drink it now.

399
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,360
If you do want to find it out,

400
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:08,000
